<section id="kde-analysis-using-adaptive-bandwidth" class="level1">
<h1>KDE Analysis using adaptive bandwidth</h1>
<p>Fixed bandwidth method is very sensitive to highly skew distribution of spatial point patterns over geographical units for example urban versus rural. One way to overcome this problem is by using adaptive bandwidth - in spatstat package, this can be derived using <code>density.adaptive()</code> function.</p>
